{{Taxobox | image = | image_caption = | domain = [[Bacteria]] | phylum = [[Planctomycetes]] | classis = [[Planctomycetacia]] | subclassis = | ordo = [[Planctomycetales]] | subordo = | familia = [[Planctomycetaceae]] | genus = '''''Telmatocola''''' | genus_authority = Kulichevskaya et al. 2012<ref name=Telmatocola>{{cite journal |last1=Parte |first1=A.C. |title=Telmatocola |website=www.bacterio.net |url=http://www.bacterio.net/telmatocola.html}}</ref> | type_species = ''Telmatocola sphagniphila''<ref name=Telmatocola/> | subdivision_ranks = [[Species]] | subdivision = ''[[Telmatocola sphagniphila|T. sphagniphila]]''<ref name=Telmatocola/> | synonyms = }}
'''''Telmatocola''''' is a genus of bacteria from the family of [[Planctomycetaceae]] with one known species (''[[Telmatocola sphagniphila]]'').<ref name=Telmatocola/><ref>{{cite journal |title=Telmatocola |website=www.uniprot.org |url=https://www.uniprot.org/taxonomy/1382832 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Parker |first1=Charles Thomas |last2=Garrity |first2=George M |title=Taxonomic Abstract for the genera. |journal=The NamesforLife Abstracts |date=1 January 2003 |doi=10.1601/tx.23140 |language=en}}</ref><ref name=PMID>{{cite journal |last1=Kulichevskaya |first1=IS |last2=Serkebaeva |first2=YM |last3=Kim |first3=Y |last4=Rijpstra |first4=WI |last5=Damsté |first5=JS |last6=Liesack |first6=W |last7=Dedysh |first7=SN |title=Telmatocola sphagniphila gen. nov., sp. nov., a novel dendriform planctomycete from northern wetlands. |journal=Frontiers in Microbiology |date=2012 |volume=3 |pages=146 |doi=10.3389/fmicb.2012.00146 |pmid=22529844|pmc=3327967 }}</ref> ''Telmatocola sphagniphila'' has been isolate from [[Sphagnum]] peat from [[Staroselsky moss]] from the [[Tver Region]].<ref name=PMID/><ref>{{cite journal |title=Details: DSM-23888 |website=www.dsmz.de |url=https://www.dsmz.de/catalogues/details/culture/DSM-23888.html |language=en}}</ref>
